> it seems like the current cvs version of Heritrix fails to build using
> sun-jdk-1.5.0_08-b03.
Good catch.  I did the warnings cleanup on jdk-1.5.0_06, which  
allowed the cast.  Stack just committed a fix tested against  
1.5.0_08, so you should be good to go.

Be advised that only minimal testing has been done on CVS head at  
this point.  A lot of code changed during the warnings cleanup, and  
I'm still verifying that things still work the way they're supposed  
to.  Please let me know if you discover any problems.

Thanks,

-Paul
